<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Contrataê · Criar conta</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
        body{font-family:Inter,Arial,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#1f1f22 0%,#0b0b0c 65%);color:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;padding:88px 24px 96px}.page-top{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;display:flex;justify-content:center;z-index:1000;padding:14px}.page-top-inner{width:min(980px,calc(100% - 24px));display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:rgba(17,17,20,.9);border:1px solid #2f3137;border-radius:16px;padding:10px 14px;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}.page-top a{color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700}.page-top .highlight{color:#ffa500}
        .shell{width:100%;max-width:1080px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:22px}
        .lead,.form-card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(28,28,30,.96),rgba(20,20,22,.98));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:24px;box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.35)}
        .lead{padding:34px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between}
        .form-card{padding:28px}
        .badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,178,30,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,178,30,.25);color:#ffd58a;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px}
        .lead h1{color:#ffb21e;font-size:38px;line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:14px}
        .lead p,.subtitle,.muted{color:#d5d5da;line-height:1.6}
        .steps{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:26px}
        .step{padding:16px;border-radius:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
        .step strong{display:block;color:#ffb21e;margin-bottom:6px}
        .title{margin:16px 0 8px;font-size:34px;color:#ffb21e}
        .panel{padding:18px;border-radius:18px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);margin-bottom:18px}
        form{display:grid;gap:16px}
        .grid-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px}
        label{display:block;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
        input,select{width:100%;background:#111114;color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 15px;font-size:15px}
        input[disabled]{background:#2a2a2f;color:#cfcfd5;cursor:not-allowed}
        .help{color:#a9a9b1;font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;line-height:1.45}
        .error{background:rgba(205,60,60,.12);border:1px solid rgba(205,60,60,.25);color:#ff9f9f;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:14px}
        .password-wrap{position:relative}
        .toggle-password{position:absolute;right:15px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);cursor:pointer;color:#999}
        .actions{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px}
        .btn{flex:1;min-width:180px;border:0;border-radius:14px;padding:15px 18px;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px}
        .btn-secondary{background:#33343a;color:#fff}
        .btn-primary{background:#ffb21e;color:#111}
        .btn-google{background:#fff;color:#111}
        .divider{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;color:#9898a1;font-size:13px}
        .divider:before,.divider:after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.09)}
        .footer{text-align:center;color:#9f9fa8;font-size:14px;margin-top:8px}
        .footer a,.link{color:#ffb21e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700}
        .bottom-nav{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:#1e1e1e;border-top:1px solid #333;display:none;justify-content:space-around;align-items:center;height:70px;z-index:1000}.nav-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:1;height:100%;color:#999;text-decoration:none;font-size:12px;gap:5px}.nav-item i{font-size:22px}.nav-item.active,.nav-item:hover{color:#ffa500} @media (max-width: 900px){.shell{grid-template-columns:1fr}.lead{order:1}.form-card{order:2}}
        @media (max-width: 640px){.grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr}body{padding:12px 12px 90px}.form-card,.lead{padding:20px}.title{font-size:28px}.lead h1{font-size:30px}.page-top{display:none}} @media (max-width: 768px){.bottom-nav{display:flex}}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-top"><div class="page-top-inner"><a href="/auth/cadastro"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Voltar</a></div></div>
    <nav class="bottom-nav safe-auth-nav">
        <a href="/" class="nav-item"><i class="fas fa-home"></i><span>Início</span></a>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="nav-item"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i><span>Voltar</span></a>
        <a href="/contato" class="nav-item"><i class="fas fa-circle-question"></i><span>Ajuda</span></a>
        <a href="/auth/cadastro" class="nav-item active"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i><span>Cadastro</span></a>
    </nav>
    <div class="shell">
        <aside class="lead">
            <div>
                <span class="badge">Cadastro <%= userType === 'professional' ? 'profissional' : 'de cliente' %></span>
                <h1><%= userType === 'professional' ? 'Crie sua conta e siga por etapas claras.' : 'Crie sua conta e encontre profissionais com facilidade.' %></h1>
                <p><%= userType === 'professional' ? 'Depois desta conta inicial, você segue para o fluxo bonito do Contrataê: dados básicos, plano, profissões, perfil e imagens.' : 'Entre rápido como cliente para buscar profissionais, comparar perfis e acompanhar suas contratações sem confusão.' %></p>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step"><strong>1. Crie sua conta</strong>Informe seu nome, e-mail e senha para liberar seu acesso.</div>
                    <% if (userType === 'professional') { %>
                    <div class="step"><strong>2. Complete o perfil</strong>Você continua no onboarding em etapas, sem perder o padrão visual.</div>
                    <div class="step"><strong>3. Publique com confiança</strong>Monte seu perfil, portfólio e envie para análise quando estiver pronto.</div>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <div class="step"><strong>2. Entre no dashboard</strong>Depois do login, você já acessa sua área de cliente.</div>
                    <div class="step"><strong>3. Contrate com praticidade</strong>Busque profissionais, veja perfis e acompanhe tudo de forma simples.</div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer"><a href="/auth/cadastro">Voltar e mudar tipo de conta</a></div>
        </aside>

        <section class="form-card">
            <span class="badge">Conta inicial</span>
            <h2 class="title">Crie sua conta</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">Seu fluxo continua do jeito certo depois desta etapa.</p>

            <% if (erro) { %>
                <div class="error"><%= erro %></div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="panel">
                <form method="POST" action="/auth/cadastro">
                    <input type="hidden" name="user_type" value="<%= userType %>">
                    <div class="grid-2">
                        <div>
                            <label>Nome completo</label>
                            <input type="text" name="full_name" required placeholder="Seu nome completo" autocomplete="name">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>E-mail</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="seu@email.com" autocomplete="email">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid-2">
                        <div>
                            <label>WhatsApp</label>
                            <input type="tel" name="phone_number" class="mask-phone" inputmode="numeric" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="(00) 00000-0000" maxlength="15">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Tipo de conta</label>
                            <input type="text" value="<%= userType === 'professional' ? 'Profissional' : 'Cliente' %>" disabled>
                            <div class="help">Quer mudar? <a class="link" href="/auth/cadastro">Clique aqui</a></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid-2">
                        <div>
                            <label>Senha</label>
                            <div class="password-wrap">
                                <input type="password" id="password-registro" name="password" required placeholder="Crie uma senha">
                                <i class="fas fa-eye toggle-password" onclick="togglePassword('password-registro', this)"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label>Confirmar senha</label>
                            <div class="password-wrap">
                                <input type="password" id="password-confirm" name="password_confirm" required placeholder="Confirme a senha">
                                <i class="fas fa-eye toggle-password" onclick="togglePassword('password-confirm', this)"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="actions">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Criar conta</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="divider">ou</div>
            <div class="actions" style="margin-top:18px;">
                <a href="/auth/google?type=<%= userType %>" class="btn btn-google"><i class="fab fa-google"></i> Cadastrar com Google</a>
            </div>

            <div class="footer" style="margin-top:18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6">Já tem uma conta? <a href="/auth/login">Entrar</a><br>Ou volte e escolha outro tipo de acesso.</div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        function togglePassword(id, icon) {
            const input = document.getElementById(id);
            if (!input) return;
            if (input.type === 'password') {
                input.type = 'text';
                icon.classList.remove('fa-eye');
                icon.classList.add('fa-eye-slash');
            } else {
                input.type = 'password';
                icon.classList.remove('fa-eye-slash');
                icon.classList.add('fa-eye');
            }
        }
    </script>
<script>document.querySelectorAll('form input').forEach((field)=>field.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{ if(e.key==='Enter'){ e.preventDefault(); }}));</script>
<script>document.querySelectorAll('.mask-phone').forEach(el=>el.addEventListener('input',e=>{e.target.value=e.target.value.replace(/\D/g,'').slice(0,11)})); document.querySelectorAll('form input').forEach(field=>field.addEventListener('keydown',e=>{ if(e.key==='Enter') e.preventDefault(); }));</script>

<script src="https://vlibras.gov.br/app/vlibras-plugin.js"></script>
<script>window.addEventListener("load", function(){ if(window.VLibras){ new window.VLibras.Widget("https://vlibras.gov.br/app"); }});</script>
</body>
</html>
